title: Suppa Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A soup restaurant that also serves vegetarian cakes. Has four different soups daily including at least one vegan soup. Also has other vegan items, of which some may not be labeled, so please inquire. Check their Facebook page for daily offerings. You can have as much bread or croutons you want, but, again, vegans please inquire. Dine-in or take away.
